messages.messageBody:
Between the proof-texting of the spanking/abuse thread (S!) and
the personal attacks, the out of order, multiple send problems of
Yahoo! are just a little extra excitement - kind of a scavenger
hunt for any clue that anyone is listening to anyone or learning
anything.
----- Original Message -----
From: "Stephanie Elms" <stephanie.elms@...>
To: <Unschooling-dotcom@yahoogroups.com>
Sent: Wednesday, October 23, 2002 10:26 PM
Subject: [Unschooling-dotcom] Argh!


| Is it just my email server or is yahoo sending all these
messages out of order?
| I keep getting replies to messages and then the messages....and
considering how
| confusing this whole thread has been anyway, I think that I am
going a little
| nuts....
|
| Stephanie E.
